    (setq gnus-namazu-command-prefix
          '(\"ssh\" \"-x\" \"remote-server\"))

This makes gnus-namazu execute \"ssh -x remote-server namazu ...\"
instead of executing \"namazu\" directly."
  :type '(repeat string)
  :group 'gnus-namazu)

